0.5 Locate your outcome

1. Upload the outcome

Starting image: click on Outcomes in the left hand mneu

Click import on the top menu.

Click anywhere to open the file chooser.

Choose the CSV file corresponding to the outcome were assessing this year. Once the file is uploaded, youll see a processing page for a moment.

Outcome upload complete

When complete, it should show:

Outcome upload complete

2. Extract the rubric

Navigate to the Rubrics section using the left-hand menu.

Outcome upload complete

Outcome upload complete

Click on Find Outcome

Choose the outcome you uploaded previoously
